<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bike Rental in Barcelona</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
      <div class="flex-container">
        <div class="bike-images">
          <img src="urban-bike1.webp" alt="bike1"><br>
          <img src="urban-bike2.webp" alt="bike2"><br>
          <img src="urban-bike3.webp" alt="bike3"><br>
          <img src="urban-bike4.webp" alt="bike4"><br>
          <img src="urban-bike5.webp" alt="bike5">
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex-child">
          <h1 style="color: #5cb245;">Urban Bike</h1><br><br>

          <b>From 8 € 2 hours</b><br><br>

          <b>Bike description:</b> from 3 to 6 gears, comfortable seat, front basket, lights (Dutch & Belgium’s style). Choose your bike. Don’t forget we offer you various size (small 50, medium 55 and higher 60) and colours (black or yellow).
          <b>Includes:</b> chain lock, helmets and Barcelona guide map.<br><br>

          <b>Requirements:</b><br><br>

          <ul>
          <li>ID or driver’s license (copy retained)</li><br>
          <li>Minimum deposit 50€ per bike (credit card or cash) better in cash to avoid bank refunding delay.</li><br>
          <li>General terms and conditions signed</li><br>
          </ul>
          <h4 style="color: #5cb245;">Choose your duration time</h4>
          <select name="urban-bike-duration" id="urban-bike-duration">
          <option value="" disabled selected>Choose your option</option>
          <option value="2hours">2 hours - 8€</option>
          <option value="4hours">4 hours - 12€</option>
          <option value="8hours">8 hours - 15€</option>
          <option value="24hours">24 hours - 18€</option>
          <option value="2days">2 days - 30€</option>
          <option value="3days">3 days - 40€</option>
          <option value="4days">4 days - 50€</option>
          <option value="5days">5 days - 60€</option>
          </select><br><br>
          <b>Choose your check-in time *</b><br><br>

          Select the best time for you to pick up your bike <br>

          <select name="urban-bike-time" id="urban-bike-time">
          <option value="" disabled selected>Choose your option...</option>
          <option value="10">10:00</option>
          <option value="11">11:00</option>
          <option value="12">12:00</option>
          <option value="13">13:00</option>
          <option value="14">14:00</option>
          <option value="15">15:00</option>
          <option value="16">16:00</option>
          <option value="17">17:00</option>
          </select><br><br>
          Choose our Shop * <br>

          Select the shop you want pick up the bikes and start your ride! <br>
          <input type="radio" name="Shop1">Shop 1 | Happy Rental Bike : Calle Roger de Flor, 5. Tel: (+34) 933 28 58 34<br>

          <select name="urban-bike-qty" id="urban-bike-qty">
          <option value="1" selected>1</option>
          <option value="2">2</option>
          <option value="3">3</option>
          </select>
          <button>Add to cart</button>
        </div> 
      </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    
  </div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
